OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHeathrow passenger charge  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto be curbed               
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Heathrow Airport has been told it      
OL,6, cannot raise its passenger charges for 
OL,7, airlines by as much as it wanted.      
OL,9,FAt present, the airport can charge up  
OL,10,Fto #23 per passenger for the cost of   
OL,11,Foperating terminals, runways, baggage  
OL,12,Fsystems and security.                  
OL,14,FIt wanted to raise the price to as much
OL,15,Fas #43 in January. However, the Civil  
OL,16,FAviation Authority has now said it will
OL,17,Fbe capped at #25 to #35 for five years.
OL,19,FAn interim figure of #30 has already   
OL,20,Fbeen set for 2022.                     
